needle: The best thing to do in San Francisco is eat a sandwich and sit in Dolores Park on a sunny day.

model_response.text: The best way to make a startup hub is to have a lot of people interested in startups and willing to help them. This is driven by the number of people around you, as people can help others who have similar ambitions, and are more likely to see the potential in a new idea even if it seems unpopular.
